{"Id":819343,"Title":"浪淘沙·蕙风翁天春楼漫笔，有记螳螂一则。言藤本花有曰夜来香者，其叶下必有一二小螳螂栖集，纤碧与叶同色，若相依为命者。曩寓金陵岁买是花，罔或爽也。词人体物之微，即小可以见大。余笑语翁若仿王桐花句例，当云妾是夜来香，郎是螳螂矣。翁深赏是语，谓天然浪淘沙佳句也。联咏足成一解","Dynasty":"清","Author":"冯幵","Context":"风雨黯横塘。著意悲凉。残荷身世误鸳鸯。花国虫天何处所，犹说情芳。妾是夜来香。郎是螳螂。花花叶叶自相当。莫向秋边寻梦去，容易繁霜。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"浪淘沙","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"e4b5ad110dd8d6335fa3ab574e180d92","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":5377025,"Sentence":"风雨黯横塘。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fēng yǔ àn héng táng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5377026,"Sentence":"著意悲凉。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"著yì bēi liáng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5377029,"Sentence":"妾是夜来香。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qiè shì yè lái xiāng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5377030,"Sentence":"郎是螳螂。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"láng shì táng láng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5377027,"Sentence":"残荷身世误鸳鸯。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"cán hé shēn shì wù yuān yāng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5377028,"Sentence":"花国虫天何处所，犹说情芳。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huā guó chóng tiān hé chǔ suǒ ，yóu shuì qǐng fāng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5377031,"Sentence":"花花叶叶自相当。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huā huā xié xié zì xiāng dāng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5377032,"Sentence":"莫向秋边寻梦去，容易繁霜。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"mò xiàng qīu biān xún mèng qù ，róng yì fán shuāng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"清"}]}